Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&HEAC93D&}（人類出現之前）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&HEAC93D&}（在浩瀚的宇宙中）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&HEAC93D&}（有無數文明）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&HEAC93D&}（索馬里斯星球）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我去告訴她 -不 不 我...\N{\fs9}-I'm just gonna go tell her. -No. No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要親自告訴她\N{\fs9}I wanna tell her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道你離開后是什么情況\N{\fs9}She knows what it's like for you to be away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶領過探索任務\N{\fs9}You've led explorations before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幾個月\N{\fs9}Not for this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-最多六星期 -她是個堅強的孩子\N{\fs9}-Six weeks at most. -She's a resilient kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但這不是補給運輸 -她會沒事的\N{\fs9}-She'll be fine. -But this isn't supply transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者跳轉到瑟林并返回 為期兩年\N{\fs9}Or a jump to Cyllene and back. It's a two-year run.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道多久\N{\fs9}I know. I know how long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fs9}-Just go. -It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難 我會去 我只是想要如何開口\N{\fs9}I'll go. I'm just thinking about what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說他們給你三倍薪水 所以我們才能負擔她的醫療\N{\fs9}Say they're tripling your salary, which is how we can afford to treat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令她康復 你沒事吧？\N{\fs9}-To cure her. -You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事\N{\fs9}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兩年...\N{\fs9}It's two years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會在這里\N{\fs9}I won't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但是當你回來 她會在\N{\fs9}I know, but when you get back, she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸\N{\fs9}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到\N{\fs9}I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？\N{\fs9}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事\N{\fs9}Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定嗎？\N{\fs9}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 我要你教我如何吹\N{\fs9}Dad, I just want you to help me with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 別太用力吹\N{\fs9}Here. Don't blow so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢 輕輕的 我想我的拇指太小了\N{\fs9}-Just easy. A little gentle. -I think my thumbs are too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的拇指很好 你只是太用力吹\N{\fs9}Your thumbs are perfect. You're just blowing too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 看我\N{\fs9}Here, watch me. Watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何你總能做好每件事？ 你令它看起來很容易\N{\fs9}Why are you so good at everything? You make it look so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很容易 你只是需要懂得技巧\N{\fs9}It is easy. You just have to know how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吹進去 往下吹\N{\fs9}-Don't blow in, blow down. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣做\N{\fs9}This is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要輕輕吹\N{\fs9}It isn't. Just blow a little gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs9}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別氣餒 再試\N{\fs9}Don't get frustrated. Try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我知道\N{\fs9}It's okay. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么？ 我知道你要離開\N{\fs9}-What do you know? -I know that you're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這是因為我\N{\fs9}And I know it's 'cause of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為你 這是為了你\N{\fs9}No, it's not because of you, it's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次要離開多久？\N{\fs9}So how long will you be gone this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐伊克探索機3703\N{\fs9}Zoic Exploratory Charter 3703.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢測到異常流星活動\N{\fs9}Unexpected meteor activity detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計算風險評估\N{\fs9}Running risk assessment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查乘客生命體征\N{\fs9}Checking passenger vitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷凍：正常\N{\fs9}Cryostasis, normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告：異常流星活動\N{\fs9}Warning. Unexpected meteor activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要手動操作\N{\fs9}Manual override required.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急著陸\N{\fs9}Emergency landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷凍箱：受損\N{\fs9}Cryochamber compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急轉發 這是運輸機3703\N{\fs9}Emergency transpondence, this is Charter 3703!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的飛船被擊中 它要墜落了！\N{\fs9}Our ship has been hit and is going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕嗎？\N{\fs9}Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌跡：偏離航線\N{\fs9}Trajectory off-course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置：不明\N{\fs9}Location unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌跡：偏離航線\N{\fs9}Trajectory off-course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置：不明\N{\fs9}Location unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌跡：偏離航線\N{\fs9}Trajectory off-course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置：不明\N{\fs9}Location unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌跡：偏離航線\N{\fs9}Trajectory off-course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷凍故障\N{\fs9}Cryogenic failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀取緊急著陸數據庫\N{\fs9}Accessing emergency landing database.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行路徑軌跡受到干擾\N{\fs9}Flight path trajectory interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前位置：不明\N{\fs9}Current location unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是佐伊克運輸機3703\N{\fs9}This is the Zoic Charter 3703.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人收到 我是遠程探索任務的唯一幸存者\N{\fs9}If anyone receives this, I'm the only survivor of a long-range exploratory mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的船被一個未記錄的小行星帶擊中\N{\fs9}My ship was struck by an undocumented asteroid belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信這些碎片來自 一個更大的隕石的一個流星團\N{\fs9}I believe the debris to be a small cluster from a much larger asteroid system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不確定\N{\fs9}But I can't be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們迫降在一個未知的星球上\N{\fs9}We've crash-landed on an uncharted celestial body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的船斷裂成兩半\N{\fs9}My ship has been severed in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定九個逃生艙被毀還有兩個失蹤了\N{\fs9}Confirmed nine escape pods have been destroyed and two are missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣是可呼吸的\N{\fs9}The atmosphere is breathable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的乘客都死了\N{\fs9}All passengers are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派救援\N{\fs9}Send help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已刪除\N{\fs9}Deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是運輸機3703 長程探索任務\N{\fs9}This is Charter 3703, long-range exploratory mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隕石碎片擊中我的船\N{\fs9}Asteroid debris field hit my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有乘客都死了 沒必要搶救\N{\fs9}All passengers are dead. No reason for recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訊息已發送\N{\fs9}Message sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三\N{\fs9}Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二\N{\fs9}two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一\N{\fs9}one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀取庫存\N{\fs9}Accessing archive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得我們前陣子去的海灘嗎？\N{\fs9}Remember when we went to the beach a while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得它有多冷嗎？\N{\fs9}And do you remember how, like--? Just cold it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面是什么感覺？\N{\fs9}What does it feel like out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&HEAC93D&}（6千5百萬年前）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&HEAC93D&}（一名探訪者墜落在）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\c&HEAC93D&}（地球）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里？\N{\fs9}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃描逃生船位置\N{\fs9}Scanning for escape vessel location.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置：不明\N{\fs9}Location unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里？\N{\fs9}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋獲佐伊克船體\N{\fs9}Section of the Zoic located.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃生船的距離 15公里\N{\fs9}Distance to escape vessel, 15 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！\N{\fs9}Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！\N{\fs9}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停！\N{\fs9}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？\N{\fs9}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字？\N{\fs9}Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.23,0:23:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 讓我們查看你是誰\N{\fs9}Okay. Let's find out who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 乘客號碼... 35\N{\fs9}Passenger number 35.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字一定是小柯\N{\fs9}Your name must be Koa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事\N{\fs9}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們看看這燙傷\N{\fs9}Here, let's look at this burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.21,0:23:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小柯 我叫米爾斯 我是這艘船的飛行員\N{\fs9}Koa, my name is Mills. I was the pilot of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.76,0:23:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們墜落之前 我正在送你們回家\N{\fs9}I was transporting you home before we crashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你在冷凍中...\N{\fs9}And you've been in cryostasis for...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:23:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久了\N{\fs9}a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導航系統故障了 我不知道我們在哪里 這里是未知的\N{\fs9}The navigation system is gone. I don't know where we are. It's uncharted.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一艘逃生船\N{\fs9}There is an escape vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.03,0:24:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在高山上\N{\fs9}But it's high above in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.87,0:24:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我們唯一離開這星球的機會\N{\fs9}That's our only chance to get you off the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.00,0:24:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面有一些異獸...\N{\fs9}There's something alien out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.42,0:24:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很危險\N{\fs9}that is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.50,0:24:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白我嗎 小柯？ “小柯” 對嗎？\N{\fs9}You understand me, Koa? I mean, it's Koa?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.35,0:24:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什么？\N{\fs9}What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.65,0:24:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么語言？\N{\fs9}What language is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.66,0:24:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能...\N{\fs9}Well, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.87,0:24:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能翻譯 我不明白\N{\fs9}I can't translate. I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.12,0:25:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不明白 我不能翻譯它\N{\fs9}No, I don't understand. I can't translate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.08,0:25:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的翻譯機壞了 像這艘船的其他東西一樣\N{\fs9}My translator's broken. Like everything else on this damn ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.63,0:25:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么語言 庫利語嗎？\N{\fs9}What is that, Kuu'ri?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.22,0:25:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕利斯卡語？\N{\fs9}Pris'ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.02,0:25:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山\N{\fs9}Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.53,0:25:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須爬上山頂\N{\fs9}We-- We must climb all the way to the top of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.53,0:25:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一半的船體在那里\N{\fs9}That's where the other half of our ship is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.70,0:25:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船\N{\fs9}Ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.74,0:25:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“山”？你明白“山”嗎？\N{\fs9}Mountain? Do you understand mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.91,0:25:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃生船 這里有一艘逃生船\N{\fs9}Escape vessel. Here's an escape vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.67,0:25:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是我們...\N{\fs9}That's where we...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.92,0:25:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里\N{\fs9}Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.34,0:25:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你離開的辦法\N{\fs9}That's how you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.13,0:25:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你回家的辦法 家\N{\fs9}-That's how you get home. -Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.35,0:25:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fs9}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.01,0:26:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-家 -是的\N{\fs9}-Home. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.82,0:26:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家\N{\fs9}Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.32,0:26:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么 你的父母嗎？\N{\fs9}What is it, your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.45,0:26:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人？\N{\fs9}Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.45,0:26:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人\N{\fs9}Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.59,0:26:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山頂上\N{\fs9}On the top of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.01,0:26:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我要告訴你的 他們在山頂上\N{\fs9}That's what I'm trying to tell you. On top of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.72,0:26:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-家人 -是的\N{\fs9}-Family. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.98,0:26:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在這里\N{\fs9}They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.45,0:27:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運輸機3703 奧納家的女兒還活著\N{\fs9}Charter 3703. The daughter of the Ona family is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.29,0:27:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個小孩 可能9歲 健康良好\N{\fs9}A child, maybe 9 years old and in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.17,0:27:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫小柯 來自上方地區 所以我們無法溝通\N{\fs9}Her name is Koa, from the upper territories, so we are unable to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.21,0:27:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的父母是乘客\N{\fs9}Her parents were passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.34,0:27:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙亡了\N{\fs9}Both deceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.01,0:27:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要帶她去遙遠的逃生船\N{\fs9}I'm taking her to an escape vessel I've located some distance away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.22,0:27:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發送求救\N{\fs9}Send help.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.18,0:27:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發送求救信號\N{\fs9}Sending distress signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.23,0:27:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這是一艘船 跟你工作時開的一樣\N{\fs9}Yeah, that's a ship. Just like the one you're driving for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.61,0:27:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發！\N{\fs9}Blast off!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.53,0:27:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的 你能相信嗎？\N{\fs9}I made it. Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.83,0:27:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校很有趣\N{\fs9}School's been pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.33,0:27:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我考得好成績 一切很順利\N{\fs9}I've been getting good grades, and everything's been going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.63,0:27:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想念你 因為我愛你\N{\fs9}I miss seeing you 'cause I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.92,0:28:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好！ 我們有一些好消息\N{\fs9}Hello. We have gotten some amazing news.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.43,0:28:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這令我很開心因為你已經在一半的行程了\N{\fs9}It's made me very happy 'cause you have made it halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.81,0:28:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的成功一半的慶祝\N{\fs9}Here is your halfway celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.69,0:28:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為你感到自豪\N{\fs9}I'm very proud on you--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.27,0:28:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為你成功一半而自豪\N{\fs9}Proud of you. For making it halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.49,0:28:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想媽已經告訴你了 有一些...\N{\fs9}I think Mom told you, but there's just a little
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.24,0:28:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一些小問題 所以...\N{\fs9}minor problem going on with me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.95,0:28:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這里真的很有趣 我認識了一些好人\N{\fs9}But it's actually really fun here and I've met some nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.25,0:28:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們令我想起你 因為你是我最好的朋友 還有...\N{\fs9}And they remind me of you because you are my greatest friend, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.33,0:28:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快回來\N{\fs9}Hurry back, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.46,0:28:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速\N{\fs9}Speed it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.50,0:28:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在真的很恨你\N{\fs9}I really hate you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.92,0:28:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不在乎我\N{\fs9}You don't even care about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.43,0:28:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你知道我...\N{\fs9}Just want you to know I...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.35,0:28:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你\N{\fs9}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.39,0:28:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很累 爸\N{\fs9}I'm so tired, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.06,0:28:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了\N{\fs9}I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.15,0:28:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘗試...\N{\fs9}I'm try--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.61,0:28:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們走吧\N{\fs9}All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.49,0:29:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fs9}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.50,0:29:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我\N{\fs9}Stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.76,0:29:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須安靜地爬上山\N{\fs9}We need to be quiet and move to the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.72,0:29:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜\N{\fs9}Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.09,0:29:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜\N{\fs9}Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.51,0:29:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和移動\N{\fs9}And move.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.56,0:29:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動\N{\fs9}Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.87,0:29:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續走\N{\fs9}Keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.64,0:30:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃生船的距離 12公里\N{\fs9}Distance to escape vessel, 12 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.24,0:30:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 握我的手\N{\fs9}Here, take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.12,0:30:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？\N{\fs9}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.00,0:30:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們走\N{\fs9}All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.34,0:32:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吃\N{\fs9}Don't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.46,0:32:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你的口直下去你的胃\N{\fs9}In your mouth down to your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.04,0:32:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了\N{\fs9}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.84,0:32:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了\N{\fs9}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.43,0:33:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！\N{\fs9}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.40,0:33:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs9}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.65,0:33:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 嘿！\N{\fs9}No. Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.74,0:33:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小柯\N{\fs9}Koa.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.28,0:34:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管它！\N{\fs9}Leave it. Leave it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.86,0:34:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了\N{\fs9}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.38,0:35:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須聽我說\N{\fs9}You have to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.13,0:35:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會害死自己\N{\fs9}You're gonna get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.72,0:36:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了！\N{\fs9}I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.18,0:36:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很累！\N{\fs9}I'm just tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.14,0:36:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很累\N{\fs9}I'm just tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.98,0:36:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我...\N{\fs9}No. I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.48,0:36:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我很累\N{\fs9}I'm saying I'm just tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.44,0:36:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很累\N{\fs9}I'm just tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.67,0:36:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝水嗎？\N{\fs9}Want some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.67,0:36:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水 沒事\N{\fs9}Water. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.94,0:37:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填滿它\N{\fs9}Well, fill it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.57,0:37:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用水填滿它\N{\fs9}Fill it with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.61,0:37:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-水 -水\N{\fs9}-Water. -Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.99,0:37:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 去平坦的那邊\N{\fs9}Here, go to the other side where it's flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.91,0:37:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水\N{\fs9}Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.03,0:38:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一朵花\N{\fs9}It's a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.32,0:38:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花 是的\N{\fs9}-Flower. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.75,0:38:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不要\N{\fs9}No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.25,0:38:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花\N{\fs9}Flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.05,0:38:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訊號干擾\N{\fs9}Signal disruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.72,0:38:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地消失\N{\fs9}Destination lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.93,0:38:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃描中\N{\fs9}Scanning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.17,0:38:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“別吃”\N{\fs9}"Don't eat."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.89,0:39:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！\N{\fs9}No, no! No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.14,0:40:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你的腿來\N{\fs9}Give me your foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.14,0:40:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力踩\N{\fs9}Push. Push.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.74,0:40:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑\N{\fs9}Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.58,0:43:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事\N{\fs9}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.79,0:43:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了嗎？\N{\fs9}Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.42,0:43:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？\N{\fs9}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.80,0:44:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小柯 我們必須走了\N{\fs9}Koa, we gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.48,0:44:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走\N{\fs9}Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.57,0:44:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs9}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.44,0:44:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們等\N{\fs9}We'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.31,0:46:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走嗎？\N{\fs9}Move?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.35,0:46:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走\N{\fs9}Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.74,0:47:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在安全了 你可以睡覺\N{\fs9}We're safe now. You can sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.32,0:47:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡\N{\fs9}Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.58,0:47:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡\N{\fs9}Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.83,0:47:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡\N{\fs9}Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.50,0:47:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家\N{\fs9}Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.06,0:47:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家在外面那里\N{\fs9}Home is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.52,0:47:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢測到異常\N{\fs9}Irregularity detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.36,0:47:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃描以識別\N{\fs9}Scanning to identify.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.12,0:47:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前無法識別異常\N{\fs9}Unable to identify irregularity at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.33,0:48:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會有更多的流星雨\N{\fs9}Could be more of the asteroid shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.51,0:48:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么？\N{\fs9}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.76,0:48:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何拿著這個？\N{\fs9}Why'd you take this?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.93,0:48:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去睡吧\N{\fs9}Go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.67,0:48:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我把它貼在...\N{\fs9}And then I'll stick it...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.64,0:48:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里...\N{\fs9}here...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.44,0:49:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在看起來有點...\N{\fs9}So now it kind of looks like it's--
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.70,0:49:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵線令它看起來很不錯\N{\fs9}The wire makes it look pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.66,0:49:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還要添加一點紅\N{\fs9}But I'm just gonna add this touch of red also.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.28,0:49:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很愛你\N{\fs9}She loved you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.74,0:49:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒受苦 她只是...\N{\fs9}She didn't suffer, she just...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.70,0:49:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是慢慢逝去\N{\fs9}She just slipped away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.05,0:50:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小柯\N{\fs9}Koa. Koa.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.51,0:50:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小柯\N{\fs9}Koa
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.30,0:50:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小柯！\N{\fs9}Koa!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.71,0:52:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？\N{\fs9}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.85,0:53:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃描替代路徑\N{\fs9}Scanning for alternate path.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.48,0:53:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢測到定向氣流\N{\fs9}Directional air current detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.64,0:55:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人\N{\fs9}Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.05,0:55:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我們就是要去那里\N{\fs9}Yeah, that's where we're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.52,0:55:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去見你的家人\N{\fs9}To see your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.89,0:55:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還不夠\N{\fs9}No, it's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.06,0:55:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山\N{\fs9}Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.73,0:56:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走？走！ 小柯\N{\fs9}Move? Move! Koa.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.73,0:56:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能移動一座山\N{\fs9}I can't move a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.57,0:56:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能 它被塞住了\N{\fs9}Look, I can't. It's blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.57,0:56:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再前進\N{\fs9}I can't go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.49,0:56:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能穿過這塊石頭\N{\fs9}I can't get past this rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.33,0:56:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣\N{\fs9}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.66,0:56:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山！\N{\fs9}Mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.29,0:56:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小柯 山\N{\fs9}Koa. Koa. Mountain.
